Description:
    Generates an image widget that displays a title, a caption and an image. It is also sortable and
    an optional link can be set that is visited when the image is clicked.

Example:
    CMS: obj_class BoxImage
    CMS: attribute title (string)
    CMS: attribute sort_key (string)
    CMS: attribute source (linklist)
    CMS: attribute caption (string)
    CMS: attribute link_to (linklist)

    `rails generate cms:widget:image`